{"title":"听战士朗诵","authors":["韩笑"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":4,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"听战士朗诵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听过多少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷人的朗诵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪一次像这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深受感动？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲技巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他并不高明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至能听出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡音很重！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一站起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有点脸红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过了一会儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却严肃庄重！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这哪里是念诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在宣誓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是捧着红心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向祖国请缨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他扬起手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像展翅的银燕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满含深情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看柳暗花明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他迈开大步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像出征的火龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声呼啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行动如风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍峨的青山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷列队；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾的绿水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匆匆集中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激怒的刀枪啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪光闪闪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起伏的心胸啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战鼓冬冬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛然立起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和他一同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去陷阵冲锋！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}